@startuml seq-prd-priority
title TN-01 — Ưu Tiên Thuyết Minh Khi Đứng Giữa 2 POI
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

actor       "Du khách"     as U
participant "EventGate"    as Gate
participant "NarrationMgr" as Nar
participant "Audio/TTS"    as Audio

U -> Gate : Enter POI-A (level=2) & POI-B (level=1)
Gate -> Gate : debounce + cooldown → pass

Gate -> Nar : HandleAsync(POI-A, level=2)
note right of Nar : Queue rỗng → POI-A thắng
Nar -> Audio : Play POI-A 🔊

Gate -> Nar : HandleAsync(POI-B, level=1)
note right of Nar
  POI-A (level=2) đang queue
  POI-B (level=1) < 2 → **loại bỏ** ✗
end note
Nar --> Gate : discarded

Audio --> U : 🔊 Chỉ nghe POI-A
note over U : POI-B không phát — không hàng đợi
@enduml
